OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill committee to
OL,4,Cconsider domestic abuse amendment
OL,6,F"I am also pleased to support the
OL,7,Famendment that ensures those exploring
OL,8,Fassisted dying are made aware of
OL,9,Fspecialist palliative and hospice care
OL,10,Foptions.
OL,12,F"It's important that people know what
OL,13,Ftheir choices are, the support is
OL,14,Favailable to them and that, for those
OL,15,Fwho still wish to pursue an assisted
OL,16,Fdeath, that there are clear,
OL,17,Faccountable, and protective steps in
OL,18,Fplace.
