OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill committee to
OL,4,Cconsider domestic abuse amendment
OL,6,F" I remain committed to working with
OL,7,Fcolleagues and stakeholders to ensure
OL,8,Fthat this Bill delivers choice,
OL,9,Fgenuine safeguards, and dignity for
OL,10,Fterminally ill adults approaching the
OL,11,Fend of their lives."
OL,13,FOn Tuesday, opposition campaigners
OL,14,Faccused the committee of
OL,15,F"'ideological' rejection of additional
OL,16,Fsafeguards", referring to an amendment
OL,17,Fto protect people with Down syndrome.
