OL,3,CAssisted dying Bill committee to
OL,4,Cconsider domestic abuse amendment
OL,6,FDr Gordon Macdonald, chief executive
OL,7,Fof Care Not Killing, said: "Today's
OL,8,Fvote against an amendment, which
OL,9,Fmerely tried to give greater
OL,10,Fprotection to those people with Down
OL,11,Fsyndrome and mitigate the negative
OL,12,Fimpact of the draft legislation, is
OL,13,Fchilling."
OL,15,FMs Leadbeater said she understood the
OL,16,Fconcerns raised and vowed these would
OL,17,Fbe addressed in guidance accompanying
OL,18,Fthe Bill.
